    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/ec991ce0b21f3290fc0107580c3899ab.apng?t=1771703201\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/ec991ce0b21f3290fc0107580c3899ab.poster.avif?t=1771703201\" class=\"bb_img\" width=630 height=200 /></picture></span><br><br>一款在后赛博朋克的迷幻霓虹城市中对抗强大的城市帮派的 2D 动作冒险游戏——如果这就是你在寻觅的游戏，《霓虹城骑士》就是你的选择！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/78b556ad897e37bc253c929c741868d5.poster.avif?t=1771703201\" width=630 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/78b556ad897e37bc253c929c741868d5.webm?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/78b556ad897e37bc253c929c741868d5.mp4?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在本作中你将扮演 Rick，一个戴着面具的佣兵，一边寻找同伴和联盟，一边打败成群的恶毒敌人、解决极富挑战性的谜题、解锁新的路径和区域，并完成引人入胜的支线任务。最后，带领你的超能帮派来解放被衰败的未来主义占领的霓虹城吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/f316683bc85e5623333c8103e8f3586c.poster.avif?t=1771703201\" width=630 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/f316683bc85e5623333c8103e8f3586c.webm?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/f316683bc85e5623333c8103e8f3586c.mp4?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>解锁各种超能力，并活用它们进行具有深度且快节奏的战斗。</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索开放式世界和许多可选的支线任务，游戏还具有四种不同的结局。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/88a304573a62a8e9199d413b0c59700a.poster.avif?t=1771703201\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/88a304573a62a8e9199d413b0c59700a.webm?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/88a304573a62a8e9199d413b0c59700a.mp4?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>沉浸于受 80 年代流行文化和电视游戏启发的复古未来派视觉和音乐风格。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/823781d22a3b299df0022d3c3cf5ef6d.poster.avif?t=1771703201\" width=630 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/823781d22a3b299df0022d3c3cf5ef6d.webm?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1102650/extras/823781d22a3b299df0022d3c3cf5ef6d.mp4?t=1771703201\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
